Text: Could someone please seed this? I have been on 89% for a week. Thanks.

The audio is Italian (which was expected). The subtitles are also Italian (which was not expected).

Hopefully I'll save someone else the 4 days of downloading I endured to figure this out.

I hope FRACTO didn't delete the file. It's a great performance of Verdi's Aida. Besides italian subs there are french, english, spanish, deutsch and chinese subtitles. I think he didn't know how to use idx/sub subtitles.
